== Shutdown ==
On April 9, 2010, it was announced that the service would be discontinued by March 31, 2011.
The service was decommissioned on March 31, 2011 and finally terminated on April 1, 2011, at 9:00 EDT.<ref>{{cite press release|url=http://cdgps.com/docs/CDGPS_Termination_Announcement.pdf |title=CDGPS Termination Announcement |format=PDF |author=Gary Sawayama |accessdate=August 3, 2012 |date=April 1, 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120204210204/http://cdgps.com/docs/CDGPS_Termination_Announcement.pdf |archivedate=February 4, 2012 |df= }}</ref>

